 Segun Ogunsanya, Chief Executive Officer and Managing Director of Airtel Nigeria.  We are excited with the partnership with 3flix as we will enable more telecoms consumers to enjoy all the fun mobile TV provides; keep abreast with latest news; follow-up with celebrities and watch their favorite sports team on the go, regardless of location,” he said.
  
Also commenting on the partnership, Chief Executive Officer of Phase3 Telecom, Stanley Jegede, said Phase3’s foresight to focus on the opportunities in emerging markets led to the creation of Coverage Broadband, and the subsequent partnership with Airtel Nigeria, to offer subscribers a distinctive mobile TV viewing service, which requires minimal data consumption. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .